data.description: Build fundamental skills and processes to develop a strong foundation in business analysis utilizing Excel. Learn the fundamentals of data construction, manipulation, summarization, analysis and presentation.

data.description: Explore the causes and consequences of inequities in the housing market. Inequities can be the result of discriminatory behavior by individuals or institutions, market forces, and government policy.  Address these issues from both historical and present-day perspectives.
data.title: FAIR HOUSING STUDIES
